# MarketNerve Build — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete production-quality iteration of the MarketNerve platform — autonomous Indian market intelligence. All changes are backward-compatible with the existing project structure.

---

## Backend (FastAPI)

### Services Upgraded

| Service | Key Improvements |
|---|---|
| **Signal Scout** ([signals.py](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/app/services/signals.py)) | Z-score & anomaly score derivation, reward-risk ratio, signal tagging (high-confidence, fresh, portfolio-relevant, high-anomaly), [signal_type](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/tests/test_signal_service.py#71-76) filter, offset pagination, [count_signals()](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/app/services/signals.py#140-151), [get_high_confidence_signals()](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/app/services/signals.py#153-156), [get_signals_by_sector()](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/app/services/signals.py#169-171) |
| **Pattern Mind** ([patterns.py](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/app/services/patterns.py)) | 10-ticker sector/cap map, expands to seed [risk_flags](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/app/services/portfolio.py#183-194), [get_pattern_by_id()](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/app/services/patterns.py#112-117), [list_patterns_by_confidence()](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/app/services/patterns.py#119-121), reward-risk in live events |
| **Portfolio Lens** ([portfolio.py](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/app/services/portfolio.py)) | ETF weight in analysis, 7 Q&A routing branches (overlap, Reliance, HDFC Bank, RBI rates, concentration, XIRR, health score), dynamic risk flags with percentages, smart recommended actions |
| **Story Engine** ([story.py](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/app/services/story.py)) | Sentiment score mapping per arc, [list_all_arcs()](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/app/services/story.py#87-89), 6-step script outline, per-arc `what_to_watch_next` |
| **IPO Intelligence** ([ipo.py](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/app/services/ipo.py)) | [get_ipo_by_name()](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/app/services/ipo.py#46-52), surfaces [cutoff_price](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/tests/test_pattern_story_health.py#205-210) + [listing_date](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/tests/test_pattern_story_health.py#211-215), 4-tier demand label |
| **Health** ([health.py](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/backend/app/services/health.py)) | 6 pipeline entries, surfaces total signals processed + uptime |

### New API Endpoints

| Method | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/signals` | Paginated signals (limit, offset, sector, signal_type, min_confidence, since) |
| `GET` | `/api/signals/latest` | High-confidence signal feed |
| `GET` | `/api/signals/sector/{sector}` | Sector-filtered signals |
| `GET` | `/api/signals/audit/{id}` | Full audit trail with z_score, tags, confidence metadata |
| `GET` | `/api/patterns/high-conviction` | Patterns above confidence threshold |
| `GET` | `/api/patterns/id/{id}` | Pattern by ID |
| `GET` | `/api/story/arcs` | All 5 story arcs |
| `GET` | `/api/ipo/active` | Active IPOs with pagination metadata |
| `GET` | `/api/ipo/{name}` | Single IPO detail |

