## Frontend (Next.js)

### Design System ([globals.css](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/apps/web/app/globals.css))
- **Fonts**: Inter + IBM Plex Mono from Google Fonts
- **Theme**: Deep dark `#09100f` with layered radial gradients
- **Tokens**: Full CSS custom property system (colors, borders, radius, shadows)
- **Animation**: `pulse-glow` keyframe for live indicator dot
- **Glassmorphism**: `backdrop-filter: blur` on panels + sticky header
- **Interactive states**: hover lift (`translateY(-2px)`) + glow shadow on cards

### Component Library ([marketnerve-shell.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/apps/web/components/marketnerve-shell.jsx))
- [MarketNerveShell](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/apps/web/components/marketnerve-shell.jsx#14-39) — sticky topbar with live wordmark pulse dot + pill nav links
- [MetricCard](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/apps/web/components/marketnerve-shell.jsx#40-49) — with tone variants (positive/warning/negative)
- [SignalCard](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/apps/web/components/marketnerve-shell.jsx#50-118) — confidence score display, Z-score bar, source chips, audit link
- [PatternCard](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/apps/web/components/marketnerve-shell.jsx#119-162) — signal strength chip, win-rate progress bar, risk flag chips
- [StoryArcCard](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/apps/web/components/marketnerve-shell.jsx#163-197) — sentiment chip, rich timeline, what-to-watch-next list
- [IpoCard](file:///c:/Users/Hp/OneDrive/Desktop/marketnerve/apps/web/components/marketnerve-shell.jsx#198-250) — GMP badge, subscription progress bar, cutoff price + listing date

### Pages Redesigned
| Page | Highlights |
|---|---|
| `/` (Home) | Hero split: priority signal + market wrap, 4-metric row, dual-column signal + pattern grid |
| `/signals` | Live indicator, filter form with number input, 2-column SignalCard grid |
| `/patterns` | Pattern count, filter form, 2-column PatternCard grid |
| `/story` | Video card with script outline timeline, quick-arc links, sentiment score panel |
| `/ipo` | Hottest IPO hero highlight, 2-column IpoCard grid |
| `/audit/[id]` | Hero signal panel, numbered reasoning steps, enrichment + confidence metadata auto-rendered |

